## 1. ECOSYSTEM REVENUE SNAPSHOT (Top Row)
- STAT CARDS (colored borders):
  - 🛒 Store revenue — rose (#F43F5E)
  - 🎓 Academy revenue — indigo (#6366F1)
  - 💼 Freelance subscriptions (student + external) — amber (#F59E0B)
  - 📢 Ad revenue (from advertiser business accounts) — teal (#14B8A6)
- PLATFORM COMMISSION: 5–10% from freelance escrow — emerald (#10B981)

## 2. SHAMCASH VERIFICATION TERMINAL (Gatekeeper)
- Unverified payment queue — all pending receipts from users
- COLUMNS: User Name · TX ID · Reported Amount · Receipt Photo (modal) · Account Type
- ACTIONS:
  - [✅ تأكيد]: activates order / freelancer account / subscription
  - [❌ إبلاغ عن خطأ]: flags and notifies user
- Works for: Students (store/sub) + Business accounts (vendor payments)

## 3. SUBSCRIPTION LIFECYCLE MONITOR
- Table: student freelancers + external freelancers (business)
- STATUS PILLS: 🟢 نشط · 🟡 ينتهي خلال 3 أيام · 🔴 منتهي
- One-click WhatsApp/inbox reminder to expiring subscribers

## 4. ESCROW HOLDING TANK
- [🔒 إجمالي الأموال المحجوزة] | [🔓 الأموال المُحررة هذا الأسبوع]
- Security rule: do not release until both parties confirm completion

## 5. GLOBAL PRICING CONFIG
- Freelance subscription fee field (currently $5 / month)
- Currency display toggle: SYP / USD
- Ad campaign pricing per zone

## 6. ANALYTICS
- Line chart: revenue last 30 days
